# Social Media System Implementation Roadmap

Based on the [Audit Report](file:///home/autcir_gmail_com/.gemini/antigravity/brain/a1c20bfe-3cb6-41c2-aa4d-11a2da50fdf0/audit_report.md), here is the plan to address the gaps.

## Sprint 1: Core Consolidation & Images
**Goal:** Stabilize existing foundation and ensure all current platforms work perfectly.

### Backend
- [ ] **LinkedIn Images**: Implement image upload in [LinkedInPublisher](file:///home/autcir_gmail_com/studiocentos_ws/apps/backend/app/domain/social/publisher_service.py#452-572). currently defaults to text-only.
- [ ] **Twitter OAuth 1.0a**: Implement proper OAuth 1.0a signing to enable posting (currently only read-only V2 is setup).

### AI Microservice
- [ ] **Scheduler Analytics**: Connect [social_media_manager.py](file:///home/autcir_gmail_com/studiocentos_ws/apps/ai_microservice/app/domain/marketing/social_media_manager.py) to real engagement data to make [suggest_optimal_times](file:///home/autcir_gmail_com/studiocentos_ws/apps/ai_microservice/app/domain/marketing/social_media_manager.py#476-512) functional.

## Sprint 2: Video Revolution
**Goal:** Enable modern short-form video content support.

### Integrations
- [ ] **TikTok**: Create `TikTokPublisher` (see audit report for skeleton).
- [ ] **YouTube Shorts**: Implement YouTube Data API v3 for Shorts upload.

### Media Processing
- [ ] **Video Converter**: Implement FFmpeg wrapper to resize/reformat video assets for vertical (9:16) format required by Reels/TikTok/Shorts.

## Sprint 3: Advanced & Local
**Goal:** Expand reach to local business and niche platforms.

### Integrations
- [ ] **Google Business Profile**: Implement API for posting updates and offers.
- [ ] **Pinterest**: Implement Pin creation.

### AI Features
- [ ] **Advanced Hashtags**: Create a dedicated `HashtagGenerator` agent in the AI service ensuring platform-specific tag density and relevance.
